WEBVTT

00:00:03.760 --> 00:00:07.416
Shah Rukh Khan: Should I listen
to my heart or mind?

00:00:07.440 --> 00:00:10.583
This is an age-old question, and I have
been looking for the answer

00:00:10.607 --> 00:00:14.447
in the books I read,
in poetry, in my films.

00:00:14.840 --> 00:00:18.560
But you know where I got the most 
interesting answer to this question?

00:00:19.440 --> 00:00:21.800
From one of India’s leading scientists.

00:00:22.600 --> 00:00:24.760
So put your hands together and welcome

00:00:24.760 --> 00:00:27.760
India’s leading neuroscientist 
Dr. Shubha Tole,

00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:33.616
But before she comes on, I would like 
to request the audience sitting at home,